title: Blackwing Starting Point Set
description:
The Blackwing Starting Point Set is the perfect way to introduce someone to Blackwing.

Each Set Includes:
  • 4 Blackwing pencils with a range of Soft, Balanced, Firm and Extra-firm graphite
  • 1 Blackwing One-Step Long Point Sharpener that creates a long, curved point that resists breakage
  • 1 pack of our Replacement Erasers to ensure your pencil is always functional
